name: My done dreams, the pending and my nightmares
description:
I walked long and I got hope finding that my dreams comed true. I started to live precious ones long way ago.

Now,
I need a change to get new results. So, only there i will be able to reach my pending dreams. Rene one day sais "if you want real change, so, walk different". Here I´m minting my first photomontage. 

Sometimes i can´t sleep at night, so i left drugs.
Only want to stop feel fear and danger of something.

Everyhing in my life is here in this image.
My art is like read my heart.
Here it is, here I am.
